<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Activation - Kafkart</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f4f4f7;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }
      .email-header {
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #fff;
        background-color: #2563eb;
      }
      .email-header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 30px;
      }
      .email-body p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .otp-wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .otp-code {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        color: #0c4a6e;
        background-color: #e0f2fe;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 6px;
      }
      .email-footer {
        font-size: 13px;
        padding: 20px 30px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #6b7280;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
      }
      .email-footer a {
        color: #2563eb;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Welcome to Kafkart!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
        <p>Thanks for signing up for Kafkart. To activate your account, please use the code below:</p>
        
        <div class="otp-wrapper">
          <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
        </div>

        <p>This code is valid for the next 5 minutes. Please enter it on the activation page.</p>
        <p>If you didn't sign up for Kafkart, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>
          Need help? Contact us at
          <a href="mailto:support@kafkart.com">support@kafkart.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
